# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.3.0] ## 2022-03-25
### Added
- Now send signed responses to the client.
- Allows to verify the model signature and the signature of the data uploaded anytime.
- Allows version to be verified, in case an outdated client is trying to use the server.

### Changed
- Move the definition of DatumTypeEnum to the proto file.
- Change the response format of BlindAiClient.upload_model.
- Change the response format of BlindAiClient.run_model.

## [0.2.2] ## 2022-03-02
### Added
- Support of remote attestation of Azure DCs_v3 VMs (this is a workaround as Azure PCS is sending expired collateral/keys).
### Changed
- Cleaned up attestation crate and fixed potential Undefined Behavior in the quote verification function.
- Upgraded Rust toolchain of the untrusted part to nightly-2021-11-01

## [0.2.1] ## 2022-02-24
### Changed
- Cleaned up warnings, used cargo fmt.

## [0.2.0] ## 2022-02-22
### Added
- Added telemetry. Can be disabled by setting the environment variable ```BLINDAI_DISABLE_TELEMETRY``` to ```1```.

## 2022-02-16
### Changed
- Changed the docker building process to enable reproducible builds.

## [0.1.0] - 2022-02-15
### Added
- Initial release
